A [[holarchy|Holarchy]] of [[squads|Autonomous Squad]] and [[chapters|Chapter]] that generates a set of products is called a value stream. The usage is similar to {{SAFe}} portfolios/value streams or {{Spotify}} / {{Iroquois Confederacy}} tribes. 

Like tribes, XSCALE value streams are limited in size by the [[Dunbar Number]]. Each [[continuously adapts|Continuous Adaptation]] its configuration of squads and chapters to its [[release plans|Release Plan]] and business objectives via a [[Stream Squad]]. 